import React from 'react'
import { Flex, Spacer,  } from "@chakra-ui/react"

function Dashboard() {
    return (
        <Flex color="white">
            <Center w="100px" bg="green.500">
                <Text>Box 1</Text>
            </Center>
            <Square bg="blue.500" size="150px">
                <Text>Box 2</Text>
            </Square>
            <Box flex="1" bg="tomato">
                <Text>Box 3</Text>
            </Box>
      </Flex>
    )
}

export default Dashboard
